Title: Snow Buddies
Writer: Robert Vince, Anna McRoberts, Kevin DiCicco (character "Air Bud"), Phil Hanley (additional comedy material), Paul Tamasy (characters), Aaron Mendelsohn (characters)
Actors: Jim Belushi, Jimmy Bennett, Lothaire Bluteau, Jason Bryden
Plot: In this spin-off of the Air Bud franchise, five pups follow an ice cream transport truck to a plane and end up flying with the ice cream shipment to Alaska. There they find a pup friend and a boy who needs five dogs for a big race.
